TITLE: Deploying LayerZero EVM Contracts (Bash)
DESCRIPTION: Uses the Hardhat LayerZero plugin (`lz:deploy`) to deploy the EVM portions of the Omnichain Application. The command prompts the user to select the target EVM networks for deployment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/layerzero-labs/devtools/blob/main/examples/oft-adapter-initia/README.md#_snippet_10

