TITLE: Deploying Contracts with LayerZero Hardhat Plugin (Bash)
DESCRIPTION: Deploys the compiled contracts to the configured target blockchains using the LayerZero Hardhat plugin task `lz:deploy`. Requires Hardhat, the LayerZero Hardhat plugin, and a properly configured `.env` file with deployer credentials and sufficient funds.
