DESCRIPTION: This command deploys the contracts to the configured blockchains using the LayerZero Hardhat plugin. It requires the `.env` file to be configured with a deployer wallet/account.
SOURCE: https://github.com/layerzero-labs/devtools/blob/main/examples/oft-adapter/README.md#_snippet_12

