DESCRIPTION: This snippet provides the commands to quickly bootstrap a new LayerZero OApp project using different Node.js package runners like npx, yarn, pnpm, and bunx. It requires having one of these package managers installed and uses the create-lz-oapp package tagged with the latest version to scaffold the project structure. The commands are intended to be run from a terminal and generate a base project ready for LayerZero smart contract development.
