TITLE: Filesystem Utilities - isFile Function in @layerzerolabs/io-devtools
DESCRIPTION: Determines if a specified filesystem path points to a file, returning true if it does. Handles errors gracefully by returning false if the path does not exist or is not a file. Utilizes Node.js filesystem methods to perform synchronous checks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/layerzero-labs/devtools/blob/main/packages/io-devtools/README.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
function isFile(path) {
  try {
    const stat = fs.statSync(path);
    return stat.isFile();
  } catch (error) {
    return false;
  }
}
```

