DESCRIPTION: Shows how to configure the `contracts` array in `layerzero.config.ts`. This example focuses on setting up `readChannelConfigs` for the Arbitrum contract, including the read library, channel ID, activity status, ULN config (executor, required/optional DVNs, threshold), and enforced options controlling gas usage and payload size for read operations.
