TITLE: Building Move Contracts for LayerZero OFT Using pnpm Bash Command
DESCRIPTION: Invokes a pnpm script to build Move VM OFT contracts specified in the given config file. The command runs the LayerZero SDK build process targeting the OFT open application type. Requires pnpm environment, Move contract sources, and a valid move.layerzero.config.ts file. Outputs compiled Move bytecode ready for deployment.
